                    <span>This author puts Jack Welch's tools to succeed in business and in life in the reader's hands.  It really hits the mark by accurately blending practicality and inspiration.  <p>Comprehensive in its coverage, this book takes you through all the phases of modern business yet it is timeless in its application.  Truely, a book to be referred to over and over.  A real gem that will age well, because the lessons learned here gain in depth and significance as time passes.<p>As a sales consultant and trainer, I find this content provides the reader a roadmap to success and enables them to control their destiny.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Jack Welch</div>
